#. type: Title ===
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Surveying Viridian Forest"
msgstr "Inspección del Bosque Viridiano"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:89
msgid "For this activity, the breakout groups will work together to examine information gathered in a survey and will then determine how to map that information to the DwC-DP tables."
msgstr "Para esta actividad, los grupos trabajarán juntos para examinar la información recogida en una encuesta y luego determinarán cómo trasladar esa información a las tablas DwC-DP."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:91
msgid "Step 1: Each group member will be assigned a role and should read through their provided role descriptions:"
msgstr "Paso 1: A cada miembro del grupo se le asignará una función y deberá leer la descripción de su función:"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:93
msgid "Professor"
msgstr "Profesor"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:94
msgid "Trainer"
msgstr "Instructor"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:95
msgid "Beedrill_01"
msgstr "Beedrill_01"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:96
msgid "Beedrill_02"
msgstr "Beedrill_02"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:97
msgid "Combee"
msgstr "Combee"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:98
msgid "Cutiefly"
msgstr "Cutiefly"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:99
msgid "Butterfree"
msgstr "Butterfree"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:100
msgid "Pikachu"
msgstr "Pikachu"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:102
msgid "Step 2: Each Pokémon has a set of information (provided on white cards).  The Pokémon and the Trainer(s) should determine which tables (the colored cards) will be used to represent the information."
msgstr "Paso 2: Cada Pokémon tiene una serie de información (proporcionada en tarjetas blancas).  El Pokémon y el Entrenador o Entrenadores deben determinar qué tablas (las cartas de color) se utilizarán para representar la información."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:104
msgid "Step 3: All the cards can be glued to the provided sheets of paper."
msgstr "Paso 3: Todas las tarjetas se pueden pegar en las hojas de papel suministradas."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:106
msgid "Step 4: Once the information and tables are arranged, the tables can be joined."
msgstr "Paso 4: Una vez que la información y las tablas están ordenadas, se pueden unir las tablas."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:108
msgid "Step 5: Remember to add your table name to your completed mapping."
msgstr "Paso 5: Recuerde añadir el nombre de la tabla a la asignación completada."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:110
msgid "Step 6: Review the other groups' https://flic.kr/s/aHBqjCxcYg[mappings^]."
msgstr "Paso 6: Revisar las https://flic.kr/s/aHBqjCxcYg[mapeos^] de los otros grupos."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:112
msgid "Step 7: Review the https://dwcdp-ipt.gbif-test.org/resource?r=viridian-forest-survey[Viridian Forest Survey of Flying Bug-type Pokémon^] dataset published on the DwC-DP test IPT."
msgstr "Paso 7: Revisar el conjunto de datos https://dwcdp-ipt.gbif-test.org/resource?r=viridian-forest-survey[Estudio del Bosque Viridian de Pokémon de tipo Bicho Volador^] publicado en el IPT de prueba de DwC-DP."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:114
msgid "If you'd like to conduct this exercise at your own institution, you can xref:attachment$SurveyingTheViridianForest-DwC-DP-Activity.zip[download all the materials] (10.5 MB) for printing on A4 paper."
msgstr "Si desea realizar este ejercicio en su propia institución, puede xref:attachment$SurveyingTheViridianForest-DwC-DP-Activity.zip[descargar todos los materiales] (10,5 MB) para imprimir en papel A4."

