#, no-wrap
msgid "Adopting DwC-DP"
msgstr "Adoptando DwC-DP"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:121
msgid "This presentation will introduce you to the resources in development and will open the discussions to assess the readiness of your node to adopt DwC-DP."
msgstr "Esta presentación le dará a conocer los recursos en desarrollo y abrirá el debate para evaluar la preparación de su nodo para adoptar DwC-DP."

